{"type":"message","id":"c1f6bfaf","parentId":"66bbd393","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:49:44.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking which agent I am, my workspace, and my current model. Let me answer based on the runtime info provided in the system prompt.\n\n- Agent: coder\n- Workspace: workspace-coder\n- Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 (default is also minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 so no difference)","thinkingSignature":"6b41ea62c926309fb39b62a245d04684afc1f4a69dd2f3a18f1be13b5b98fc3a"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n我是 **coder** agent，工作空间是 `workspace-coder`，当前模型是 **MiniMax-M2.7**（默认模型也是 MiniMax-M2.7，没有切换）。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90,"output":119,"cacheRead":18509,"cacheWrite":993,"totalTokens":19711,"cost":{"input":0.000027,"output":0.0001428,"cacheRead":0.00055527,"cacheWrite":0.00011915999999999999,"total":0.00084423}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774345779313}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed9d3db1","parentId":"c1f6bfaf","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:22:00.924Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b531daeb12870c4274d760ce25c7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 22:22 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b531daeb12870c4274d760ce25c7]\nou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd: 如何写一个 ai agent"}],"timestamp":1774362120920}}
{"type":"message","id":"09023678","parentId":"ed9d3db1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:22:21.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to write an AI agent. This is a broad question - I should give a concise but useful overview. Let me think about what a good answer looks like.\n\nKey components of an AI agent:\n1. LLM (the brain)\n2. Tools/actions (what it can do)\n3. Memory (how it persists context)\n4. Loop/iteration mechanism (often called \"agent loop\" or \"reasoning loop\")\n\nI should give a practical overview without being too verbose. This person seems to be asking in Chinese, so I'll respond in Chinese.","thinkingSignature":"5c582fceb054ed13111777d3ce8d0d230c54819acc69ac0bc7c2f6cbf93383df"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n写一个 AI Agent 主要有这几个核心组件：\n\n**1. LLM（大模型）**\n选择模型是第一步——GPT-4、Claude、Qwen、MiniMax 等。负责\"思考\"和决策。\n\n**2. Tools（工具）**\n让模型能\"行动\"——搜索、读写文件、执行代码、调用 API 等。工具越丰富，能力越强。\n\n**3. Memory（记忆）**\n上下文管理：短期用对话历史，长期用向量数据库或文件存储。\n\n**4. Agent Loop（代理循环）**\n典型的 while 循环：感知 → 思考 → 行动 → 反馈 → 重复。常见模式有：\n- **ReAct**：思考 + 行动 + 观察\n- **Plan-and-Execute**：先规划再执行\n- **Single-Step**：单步决策（简单场景）\n\n**最简骨架（Python 伪代码）：**\n```python\nwhile True:\n    observation = get_input()\n    thought = llm.think(observation, tools, memory)\n    if thought.action == \"finish\":\n        break\n    result = execute_tool(thought.tool, thought.args)\n    memory.add(observation, thought, result)\n```\n\n**实际框架推荐：**\n- **LangGraph**（LangChain 母公司）— 最主流，够灵活\n- **AutoGen**（微软）— 多 Agent 协作强\n- **CrewAI** — 上手最简单，Role-Based\n- **OpenClaw**（就是你现在用的 😄）— 开箱即用\n\n你想专注哪个方向？我可以帮你深入讲。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90,"output":450,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":19806,"totalTokens":20346,"cost":{"input":0.000027,"output":0.00054,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0023767199999999997,"total":0.0029437199999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774362120923}}
