{"type":"message","id":"66426b1a","parentId":"d7221d33","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:23:52.799Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b531da9b7253cc3a519c14425da9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 22:23 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b531da9b7253cc3a519c14425da9]\nou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd: 写一个ai agent ，应该关注哪些方面"}],"timestamp":1774362232797}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac26a522","parentId":"66426b1a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:24:06.698Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about what aspects to focus on when writing an AI agent. I'll give a structured, opinionated answer.","thinkingSignature":"71da27a203fc39d40451b31bc7e9c708f6a7c2540464c0edbcb3cb70a555c165"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n构建 AI Agent 时，这几个方面最值得投入：\n\n**🔧 核心能力**\n- **工具设计** — 工具是 Agent 的手脚，要粒度合适、职责单一、错误可处理\n- **Prompt 工程** — 指令清晰度直接影响输出质量，往往比调模型参数更有效\n- **模型选择** — 够用就行，别为用不到的参数量买单\n\n**🧠 记忆系统**\n- **短期记忆** — 对话历史怎么管理（全部塞还是压缩？）\n- **长期记忆** — 什么要记住、用什么方式（向量检索？结构化存储？）\n- **上下文窗口** — 越大越贵，要设计截断策略\n\n**🔄 Agent Loop 设计**\n- **循环控制** — 怎么防止死循环（max iterations、停止信号）\n- **错误恢复** — 工具调用失败后怎么办、重试几次\n- **路径规划** — 单步执行还是规划后执行\n\n**🛡️ 可靠性**\n- **确定性** — 同样的输入要有一致的结果\n- **可观测性** — 日志、trace、每步在干什么要能看清楚\n- **安全边界** — destructive 操作要有确认机制\n\n**📊 评估 & 迭代**\n- **评测集** — 没有 benchmark 就没法迭代\n- **Case 分析** — 失败case比成功case更有价值\n\n你目前在哪个阶段？我可以针对性地聊。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90,"output":331,"cacheRead":20261,"cacheWrite":439,"totalTokens":21121,"cost":{"input":0.000027,"output":0.0003972,"cacheRead":0.00060783,"cacheWrite":0.00005268,"total":0.00108471}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774362232799}}
{"type":"message","id":"63f86b11","parentId":"ac26a522","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:25:31.113Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b531da36c8ca8c3b2f95c7d22467\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 22:25 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b531da36c8ca8c3b2f95c7d22467]\nou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd: 才开始了解，你实质性的一步步给我过一下"}],"timestamp":1774362331111}}
{"type":"message","id":"354b08ca","parentId":"63f86b11","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:25:58.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a practical step-by-step guide for getting started with AI agents, from scratch. Let me think about what would be most helpful and structured.\n\nSince they're just starting to understand, I should:\n1. Start very fundamental\n2. Be practical and concrete\n3. Go step by step\n4. Maybe suggest a simple project to start with\n\nLet me think about the best order:\n1. First understand what an AI agent is conceptually\n2. Choose your stack (framework + model)\n3. Set up the environment\n4. Build the simplest possible agent\n5. Add tools\n6. Add memory\n7. Test and iterate\n\nI should be practical and give actual steps they can follow.","thinkingSignature":"3666c8bdfa7bd7b7aa2580250cf094a635acfd0c4f828a844c5e8f1bc89f233c"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n好，从零开始，一步一步来：\n\n---\n\n## 第一步：搞懂概念（5分钟）\n\n先在脑子里形成清晰画面：\n\n- **LLM** = 大脑，负责思考\n- **Tools** = 手脚，负责执行（搜索、读文件、执行代码等）\n- **Loop** = 循环：输入→思考→行动→结果→再思考→...\n\nAgent 就是\"能自己决定做什么、并调用工具去执行\"的程序。\n\n---\n\n## 第二步：选框架和模型\n\n**框架（二选一）：**\n| 框架 | 适合 |\n|------|------|\n| **CrewAI** | 刚入门，概念简单，上手最快 |\n| **LangGraph** | 想做复杂逻辑，需要更多控制 |\n\n**模型：**\n- 国内用：**Qwen（通义）**、**MiniMax**、**GLM**（中文好，API 便宜）\n- 国外用：**GPT-4o**、**Claude 3.5**\n\n推荐起步： crewai + qwen2.5\n\n---\n\n## 第三步：搭环境\n\n```bash\n# 创建项目目录\nmkdir my-agent && cd my-agent\n\n# 创建虚拟环境\npython -m venv venv\nsource venv/bin/activate  # Mac/Linux\n# venv\\Scripts\\activate   # Windows\n\n# 安装依赖（以 crewai 为例）\npip install crewai crewai-tools\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第四步：写最简 Agent（30行代码）\n\n创建 `agent.py`：\n\n```python\nfrom crewai import Agent, Task, Crew\n\n# 定义一个能搜索网页的工具\nsearch_agent = Agent(\n    role=\"搜索助手\",\n    goal=\"根据用户问题搜索相关信息\",\n    backstory=\"你是一个专业的搜索助手，擅长从网上找到准确信息\",\n    tools=[]  # 先不加工具，看纯对话效果\n)\n\n# 定义任务\ntask = Task(\n    description=\"用户问：什么是AI Agent？\",\n    agent=search_agent\n)\n\n# 启动\ncrew = Crew(agents=[search_agent], tasks=[task])\nresult = crew.kickoff()\nprint(result)\n```\n\n运行：\n```bash\npython agent.py\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第五步：给 Agent 加工具\n\ncrewai 自带一些工具，直接用：\n\n```python\nfrom crewai import Agent\nfrom crewai_tools import SerpAPITool, FileReadTool\n\n# 搜索工具\nsearch_tool = SerpAPITool()\n\nresearcher = Agent(\n    role=\"研究员\",\n    goal=\"搜集并整理信息\",\n    tools=[search_tool],  # 给它加一个搜索工具\n    backstory=\"你是一个严谨的研究员\"\n)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第六步：多 Agent 协作\n\n真正强大的地方——多个 Agent 分工合作：\n\n```python\nresearcher = Agent(role=\"研究员\", goal=\"搜集信息\", tools=[search_tool])\nwriter = Agent(role=\"作家\", goal=\"把研究结果写成文章\")\n\ncrew = Crew(agents=[researcher, writer], tasks=[...], process=\"sequential\")\n# process=\"sequential\" = 串行：研究员做完 → 作家接着做\n```\n\n---\n\n## 下一步做什么\n\n1. 把上面代码跑通\n2. 换一个自己的任务（比如\"帮我查今天天气\"）\n3. 加一个自定义工具（读本地文件、查数据库等）\n\n你现在 Python 熟吗？需要我帮你把环境搭起来，还是先深入讲某个步骤？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90,"output":862,"cacheRead":20449,"cacheWrite":827,"totalTokens":22228,"cost":{"input":0.000027,"output":0.0010344,"cacheRead":0.00061347,"cacheWrite":0.00009923999999999999,"total":0.0017741099999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774362331113}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ee18560","parentId":"354b08ca","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:27:32.557Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b531dbbf400a8c2ef99bc8690598\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 22:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b531dbbf400a8c2ef99bc8690598]\nou_930ed7a70e55cdc26722683f4d7d00bd: 再重新设计一下 要灵活可配 扩展性好"}],"timestamp":1774362452554}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ca73c84","parentId":"9ee18560","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:28:31.166Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a more flexible, configurable, and extensible AI agent design. This is a more advanced architectural discussion. Let me think about what makes an agent architecture truly flexible and extensible:\n\n1. **Tool abstraction** - Tools should be plugins, easy to add/remove\n2. **Agent configuration** - Agents should be configurable via configs (not hardcoded)\n3. **Memory modularity** - Different memory backends\n4. **LLM agnostic** - Switch models easily\n5. **Loop strategy pattern** - Different execution strategies\n6. **Dependency injection** - Components loosely coupled\n\nLet me design a clean, practical architecture.","thinkingSignature":"63779a7da6a32b4a0109867897deb5177c169ccf612107444dd5ac7a0b5761d7"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n好，做一个真正能用在生产环境的设计。\n\n---\n\n## 核心架构图\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                  Agent Engine               │\n│                                             │\n│  ┌─────────┐   ┌─────────┐   ┌─────────┐   │\n│  │  LLM    │   │ Memory  │   │  Tools  │   │\n│  │ Manager │   │ Manager │   │ Registry│   │\n│  └────┬────┘   └────┬────┘   └────┬────┘   │\n│       │             │             │         │\n│       └─────────────┼─────────────┘         │\n│                     │                       │\n│              ┌──────▼──────┐                │\n│              │  Agent Core │                │\n│              │   (Loop)    │                │\n│              └──────┬──────┘                │\n│                     │                       │\n│              ┌──────▼──────┐                │\n│              │  Executor   │                │\n│              └─────────────┘                │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\nmy_agent/\n├── config/\n│   ├── agents.yaml        # Agent 配置（角色、目标、工具）\n│   ├── llms.yaml           # 模型配置（多模型切换）\n│   └── tools.yaml          # 工具注册\n├── tools/\n│   ├── __init__.py\n│   ├── base.py             # 工具基类\n│   ├── search.py\n│   ├── file_ops.py\n│   └── custom_tool.py      # 你的自定义工具\n├── core/\n│   ├── llm_manager.py      # LLM 管理（切换模型）\n│   ├── memory_manager.py   # 记忆管理\n│   ├── tool_registry.py   # 工具注册中心\n│   ├── agent.py            # Agent 核心类\n│   └── executor.py         # 执行器\n├── agents/\n│   └── researcher.py        # 具体 Agent 定义\n├── config.yaml             # 主配置\n├── main.py                 # 入口\n└── requirements.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第一步：工具基类（插件机制）\n\n所有工具继承同一个基类，类型安全、便于扩展：\n\n```python\n# tools/base.py\nfrom abc import ABC, abstractmethod\nfrom typing import Any, Dict\n\nclass BaseTool(ABC):\n    name: str                    # 唯一标识\n    description: str             # 描述（让 LLM 知道什么时候用它）\n    \n    @abstractmethod\n    def execute(self, **kwargs) -> Any:\n        \"\"\"执行逻辑，子类实现\"\"\"\n        pass\n    \n    def validate(self, **kwargs) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"参数校验，可选实现\"\"\"\n        return True\n```\n\n新建工具只需继承，不用动核心代码：\n\n```python\n# tools/search.py\nfrom tools.base import BaseTool\n\nclass SearchTool(BaseTool):\n    name = \"web_search\"\n    description = \"搜索互联网获取最新信息\"\n    \n    def execute(self, query: str, **kwargs) -> str:\n        # 实际搜索逻辑\n        return f\"搜索结果：{query} ...\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第二步：工具注册中心（插件发现）\n\n自动发现 `tools/` 下的所有工具，配置驱动：\n\n```python\n# core/tool_registry.py\nimport yaml\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Dict\n\nclass ToolRegistry:\n    def __init__(self, config_path: str):\n        self._tools: Dict[str, BaseTool] = {}\n        self._load_from_config(config_path)\n    \n    def _load_from_config(self, config_path: str):\n        with open(config_path) as f:\n            config = yaml.safe_load(f)\n        \n        for tool_cfg in config.get(\"tools\", []):\n            tool_class = self._import_tool(tool_cfg[\"class\"])\n            self._tools[tool_cfg[\"name\"]] = tool_class(**tool_cfg.get(\"params\", {}))\n    \n    def _import_tool(self, class_path: str):\n        module_path, class_name = class_path.rsplit(\".\", 1)\n        module = __import__(module_path, fromlist=[class_name])\n        return getattr(module, class_name)\n    \n    def get(self, name: str) -> BaseTool:\n        return self._tools[name]\n    \n    def list_tools(self):\n        return [(t.name, t.description) for t in self._tools.values()]\n```\n\n配置文件声明式：\n\n```yaml\n# config/tools.yaml\ntools:\n  - name: web_search\n    class: tools.search.SearchTool\n    params:\n      api_key: ${SEARCH_API_KEY}   # 环境变量引用\n      max_results: 5\n  - name: file_read\n    class: tools.file_ops.FileReadTool\n    params:\n      base_dir: ./workspace\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第三步：LLM 管理器（多模型切换）\n\n一个接口，多个实现：\n\n```python\n# core/llm_manager.py\nimport yaml\nfrom abc import ABC, abstractmethod\nfrom typing import Optional\n\nclass BaseLLM(ABC):\n    @abstractmethod\n    def chat(self, messages: list, **kwargs) -> str:\n        pass\n\nclass LLMManager:\n    def __init__(self, config_path: str):\n        with open(config_path) as f:\n            self._config = yaml.safe_load(f)\n        self._current = self._config[\"default\"]\n        self._instances = {}\n    \n    def set_model(self, name: str):\n        \"\"\"运行时切换模型\"\"\"\n        self._current = name\n    \n    def chat(self, messages: list, **kwargs) -> str:\n        llm = self._get_instance(self._current)\n        return llm.chat(messages, **kwargs)\n    \n    def _get_instance(self, name: str) -> BaseLLM:\n        if name not in self._instances:\n            cfg = self._config[\"models\"][name]\n            llm_class = self._load_class(cfg[\"class\"])\n            self._instances[name] = llm_class(**cfg.get(\"params\", {}))\n        return self._instances[name]\n```\n\n模型配置：\n\n```yaml\n# config/llms.yaml\ndefault: qwen2.5\n\nmodels:\n  qwen2.5:\n    class: llms.qwen.QwenLLM\n    params:\n      model: qwen2.5-7b\n      api_key: ${DASHSCOPE_API_KEY}\n      base_url: https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com\n      \n  gpt4o:\n    class: llms.openai.OpenAILLM\n    params:\n      model: gpt-4o\n      api_key: ${OPENAI_API_KEY}\n```\n\n切换模型一行代码：`llm_manager.set_model(\"gpt4o\")`\n\n---\n\n## 第四步：Agent 核心（可插拔设计）\n\n```python\n# core/agent.py\nfrom typing import List, Optional\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\n\n@dataclass\nclass AgentConfig:\n    name: str\n    role: str\n    goal: str\n    backstory: str\n    tools: List[str]          # 工具名列表，由 registry 解析\n    llm: Optional[str] = None  # 可选，指定模型\n\nclass Agent:\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        config: AgentConfig,\n        llm_manager: LLMManager,\n        tool_registry: ToolRegistry,\n        memory_manager: MemoryManager\n    ):\n        self.config = config\n        self.llm_manager = llm_manager\n        self.tools = {name: tool_registry.get(name) for name in config.tools}\n        self.memory = memory_manager\n    \n    def think(self, user_input: str) -> dict:\n        # 1. 构造 prompt（包含工具描述）\n        prompt = self._build_prompt(user_input)\n        \n        # 2. 调用 LLM\n        response = self.llm_manager.chat(prompt)\n        \n        # 3. 解析 LLM 返回（决定用哪个工具 + 参数）\n        decision = self._parse_response(response)\n        return decision\n    \n    def act(self, decision: dict):\n        if decision[\"type\"] == \"tool\":\n            tool = self.tools[decision[\"tool\"]]\n            return tool.execute(**decision[\"params\"])\n        return decision[\"content\"]\n    \n    def run(self, user_input: str, max_turns: int = 10):\n        self.memory.add(\"user\", user_input)\n        \n        for turn in range(max_turns):\n            decision = self.think(user_input)\n            \n            if decision[\"type\"] == \"finish\":\n                final = decision[\"content\"]\n                self.memory.add(\"assistant\", final)\n                return final\n            \n            result = self.act(decision)\n            self.memory.add(\"tool\", result)\n            user_input = f\"上一步结果：{result}，请继续\"\n        \n        return \"达到最大轮次限制\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第五步：记忆管理（模块化）\n\n```python\n# core/memory_manager.py\nfrom abc import ABC, abstractmethod\n\nclass BaseMemory(ABC):\n    @abstractmethod\n    def add(self, role: str, content: str): pass\n    @abstractmethod\n    def get_history(self) -> list: pass\n\nclass SimpleMemory(BaseMemory):\n    \"\"\"简单内存：只保留最近 N 条\"\"\"\n    def __init__(self, max_turns: int = 20):\n        self.max_turns = max_turns\n        self._history = []\n    \n    def add(self, role: str, content: str):\n        self._history.append({\"role\": role, \"content\": content})\n        if len(self._history) > self.max_turns:\n            self._history.pop(0)\n    \n    def get_history(self):\n        return self._history\n```\n\n以后要换向量检索记忆？写一个新类继承 `BaseMemory`，Agent 代码不用改：\n\n```python\nclass VectorMemory(BaseMemory):\n    def __init__(self, embedding_model, vector_db):\n        ...\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第六步：配置组装（主入口）\n\n```python\n# main.py\nimport yaml\nfrom core.agent import Agent, AgentConfig\nfrom core.llm_manager import LLMManager\nfrom core.tool_registry import ToolRegistry\nfrom core.memory_manager import SimpleMemory\n\n# 加载配置\nwith open(\"config/agents.yaml\") as f:\n    agents_config = yaml.safe_load(f)\n\n# 初始化组件\nllm_mgr = LLMManager(\"config/llms.yaml\")\ntool_reg = ToolRegistry(\"config/tools.yaml\")\nmemory = SimpleMemory(max_turns=30)\n\n# 创建 Agent\ncfg = AgentConfig(**agents_config[\"researcher\"])\nagent = Agent(cfg, llm_mgr, tool_reg, memory)\n\n# 运行\nresult = agent.run(\"帮我查一下今天有什么新闻\")\nprint(result)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 这个设计的优势\n\n| 维度 | 实现方式 |\n|------|----------|\n| **新增工具** | 写一个类，添加到 `tools.yaml` |\n| **切换模型** | 改 `llms.yaml`，或一行代码 |\n| **新增 Agent** | 在 `agents.yaml` 写配置，不改代码 |\n| **换记忆策略** | 换 `MemoryManager` 的实现类 |\n| **运行时调整** | 配置热加载，不用重启 |\n\n---\n\n你想先做哪一块？我可以帮你把代码骨架搭起来。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90,"output":2514,"cacheRead":21036,"cacheWrite":1223,"totalTokens":24863,"cost":{"input":0.000027,"output":0.0030168,"cacheRead":0.0006310799999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00014675999999999998,"total":0.0038216400000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774362452556}}
